narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I very much enjoyed this course! This class dealt with a wide variety of topics. We learned a great deal about the Indonesian culture and traditions in various cities, as well as honed in on our Indonesian language skills.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course was very worthwhile and informative. I immensely enjoyed all of the guest speakers' presentations. The Indonesian community as a whole contains some of the nicest, most genuine people. I enjoyed every aspect of this class. My only suggestion is that I wish we had more class time (as in 2 classes a week in addition to ngobrol-ngobrol). I truly loved this class!

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would absolutely recommend this course to another student. Bu Dinny is an excellent professor and an even better person. I learned a great deal about the Indonesian culture during the course of this class.
